Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:03.20,Title,,0,0,0,,THE GREAT BRITISH CODING RELAY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:06.70,Body,,0,0,0,,An ambulance arrives.\NA patient episode begins.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:06.70,0:00:09.80,Detail,,0,0,0,,The hi-vis pigeon has already\Nopened an incident ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:13.50,Title,,0,0,0,,DOCTORS TREAT. THEN DOCUMENT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:17.20,Body,,0,0,0,,Notes. Scans. Discharge summaries.\NMore notes.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:17.20,0:00:19.80,Detail,,0,0,0,,And one mysterious sentence\Ncopied forward since Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:23.50,Title,,0,0,0,,ENTER: CLINICAL CODING
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:27.20,Body,,0,0,0,,Across NHS trusts, coding teams\Ncan run to 30+ specialists.\NThey read the whole episode.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.20,0:00:29.80,Detail,,0,0,0,,Years to master. Labour-intensive.\NRipe for careful automation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.80,Title,,0,0,0,,CLINICAL CHAOS → ICD-10 + OPCS-4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:37.20,Body,,0,0,0,,The codes drive reimbursement,\Nepidemiology and planning.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.20,0:00:39.80,Detail,,0,0,0,,No codes, no money. Finance starts\Nbreathing into a paper bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.10,0:00:43.30,Title,,0,0,0,,AI COULD HELP. TINY PROBLEM: DATA.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:46.00,Body,,0,0,0,,Patient records are sensitive.\NYou cannot simply download a ward.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:46.00,0:00:49.80,Detail,,0,0,0,,USA: MIMIC-IV — reusable, US-specific.\NUK: OPCS-4, governance, tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.10,0:00:53.10,Title,,0,0,0,,SO WE BUILT THE TEST TRACK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.00,0:00:56.20,Body,,0,0,0,,UK-specific synthetic training episodes\N+ a benchmark for coding AI products.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.20,0:00:58.20,Detail,,0,0,0,,Catch hallucinations before they invoice anyone.
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.10,0:00:59.85,Finale,,0,0,0,,THE MVP: EPICODE-Bench\NAll the coding drama. None of the data breach.
